        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3590237973" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13841347244279333203">Worth it for <i>Aurélia</i>, which describes the author&apos;s hallucinatory descent into madness and was influential to the surrealists and other writers like René Daumal and Antonin Artaud, but the other texts are not worth your time.</span>
  <span id="freeText13841347244279333203" style="display:none">Worth it for <i>Aurélia</i>, which describes the author's hallucinatory descent into madness and was influential to the surrealists and other writers like René Daumal and Antonin Artaud, but the other texts are not worth your time.</span>
